'''派珀PA-44'''是由[[派珀航空|派珀航空]]制造的轻型雙引擎[[螺旋槳飛機|螺旋槳飛機]]，该飞机由{{Link-en|Piper PA-28|Piper PA-28 Cherokee}}单引擎飞机发展而来，主要用于多引擎飞行训练。<ref name="NewPiper"/><ref name="Foster">Montgomery, MR & Gerald Foster: ''A Field Guide to Airplanes, Second Edition'', page 92. Houghton Mifflin Company, 1992. ISBN 0-395-62888-1</ref>

==设计和开发==
第一架生产的该型飞机配备了两个180[[马力|马力]]（135[[千瓦|千瓦]]）的莱康明O-360-E1A6D系列引擎，而右侧发动机采用[[反向旋转螺旋桨|反向旋转螺旋桨]]，这个特性使飞机在发动机需要被关机或出现故障的情况下更加可控。此飞机在1978年3月10日首次取得[[适航许可|适航许可]]，此后在1978年年底推出。
该飞机具有类似于[[Piper_PA-28|Piper PA-28]]的高T型[[尾翼|尾翼]]。<ref name="NewPiper">{{cite web |url = http://www.newpiper.com/aircraft/seminole/specifications.asp |title = Seminole Price and Standard Equipment |date = undated |author = New Piper Aircraft |accessdate = 2007-10-02 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071023061708/http://www.newpiper.com/aircraft/seminole/specifications.asp |archivedate = 2007-10-23 }}</ref><ref name="A19SO">{{cite web|url = http://www.airweb.faa.gov/Regulatory_and_Guidance_Library/rgMakeModel.nsf/0/f07de52f6061c8cc8625720a0054ef4f/$FILE/A19SO.pdf|format = PDF|title = TYPE CERTIFICATE DATA SHEET NO. A19SO Revision 10|accessdate = 2008-09-09|last = Federal Aviation Administration|authorlink = |date = August 2006|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110608084840/http://www.airweb.faa.gov/Regulatory_and_Guidance_Library/rgMakeModel.nsf/0/f07de52f6061c8cc8625720a0054ef4f/$FILE/A19SO.pdf|archive-date = 2011-06-08|dead-url = yes}}</ref>

